Homework 1 Readme File

Basic Information
PLATFORM: OSX
OS Version: OSX Yosemite 10.10.1
Build Environment: Xcode
Build Environment Version: Xcode 6.1.1
Language: C++
External Libraries Used (e.g., GLUT, GL, etc.): GLUT, GL, GLU, math.h, ctime, stdio, stdlib, iostream, fstream

Build Instructions
1. Unzip File
2. Open Folder "MP1/DancingI"
3. Open File "MP1/ Dancing I.xcodeproj"
4. Run

OR

Simply run the Executable
1. Unzip File
2. Open Folder "MP1/DancingI"
3. Open Folder "MP1/DancingI"
4. Double Click Executable "MP1/DancingI"

Controls
's' Toggles movement of Block I
'x' Exits the program
'w' Toggles Wireframe Mode

Video Demo
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4FcOI2YvvfI

